data.text:
What is the meaning of the name Leona?

The name Leona is primarily a female name of Italian origin that means Lion.

Feminine form of Leon. Also a Hebrew name, Leeona, meaning "my strength." Leona Lewis, singer.

People who like the name Leona also like:

Violet, Fiona, Luna, Ophelia, Aurora, Charlotte, Amelia, Oliver, Owen, Leo, Silas, Liam, Sebastian, Benjamin
